urce":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recr2ic6Ws3R14a5I","label":"part of"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"rec3qiPi8JN2h86Mj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"rec1ZMFtfbEvoGC73","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recUn6eVJDoG4xI0j","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recGEuLOhqY6PsgzE","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recabsaJkxxtgdUSt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recesqn5JDm6ZwKE5","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"reczPjeq0UdahiRrn","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recq2rEmFeuPt4ouE","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"rec1NgBQ2zMeIsFyT","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recVMgLyBVZ3c8jaf","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recbaKaeB0APyZYLy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recuaojGkwInnfYgK","target":"recQ1bj3p4Lj5MYY6","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"reclYkldZoVYdCjyF","ref":"Isa.16.1","text":"Send ye the lamb to the ruler of the land from Sela to the wilderness, unto the mount of the daughter of Zion.","year":-726},{"id":"recibdPgKUL1C8p2J","ref":"Isa.16.2","text":"For it shall be, that, as a wandering bird cast out of the nest, so the daughters of Moab shall be at the fords of Arnon.","year":-726},{"id":"recgv6pZcwF8biRXA","ref":"Isa.16.3","text":"Take counsel, execute judgment; make thy shadow as the night in the midst of the noonday; hide the outcasts; bewray not him that wandereth.","year":-726},{"id":"recJCcgsKnnFrHzNA","ref":"Isa.16.4","text":"Let mine outcasts dwell with thee, Moab; be thou a covert to them from the face of the spoiler: for the extortioner is at an end, the spoiler ceaseth, the oppressors are consumed out of the land.","year":-726},{"id":"rech359IAFVNFd0r7","ref":"Isa.16.5","text":"And in mercy shall the throne be established: and he shall sit upon it in truth in the tabernacle of David, judging, and seeking judgment, and hasting righteousness.","year":-726},{"id":"recGDBp28Gx2nx0vl","ref":"Isa.16.6","text":"We have heard of the pride of Moab; he is very proud: even of his haughtiness, and his pride, and his wrath: but his lies shall not be so.","year":-726},{"id":"recaNp9383XOiX4ww","ref":"Isa.16.7","text":"Therefore shall Moab howl for Moab, every one shall howl: for the foundations of Kirhareseth shall ye mourn; surely they are stricken.","year":-726},{"id":"recpV10sydLH60mLe","ref":"Isa.16.8","text":"For the fields of Heshbon languish, and the vine of Sibmah: the lords of the heathen have broken down the principal plants thereof, they are come even unto Jazer, they wandered through the wilderness: her branches are stretched out, they are gone over the sea.","year":-726}]}
